                        招生小组
                    </td>
                    <td class='l-table-edit-td' style='text-align: left; width: 160px'>
                        <input name='f_TeamId2' type='text' id='f_TeamId2' ltype='text' />
                        <input name='TeamId2' type='hidden' id='TeamId2' />
